{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Boolean","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean/toString\"><code>Boolean.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean/valueOf\"><code>Boolean.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Herança:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;objeto&nbsp;<strong><code>Boolean</code></strong>&nbsp;é um objeto wrapper para um valor booleano.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>new Boolean([<var>value</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd>Opcional. O valor inicial do objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean.</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"descrição","title":"Descrição","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O valor passado como primeiro parâmetro é convertido para um valor boleano, se necessário. Se o valor é omitido ou&nbsp;é&nbsp;<code>0</code>, <code>-0</code>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a>, <code>false</code>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> ou é uma string vazia(<code>\"\"</code>), o objeto terá um valor inicial de <code>false</code>. Todos outros valores, incluindo qualquer objeto ou string <code>\"false\"</code>, &nbsp;criam um objeto com valor inicial &nbsp;<code>true</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Não confunda os valores&nbsp;primitivos&nbsp;Boolean&nbsp;<code>true</code> e&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;com os valores&nbsp;<code>true</code> and <code>false</code>&nbsp;do objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Qualquer objeto cujo o valor não é&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> ou&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a>, incluindo um objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;que o valor seja&nbsp;<code>false</code>, é avaliado para <code>true</code>&nbsp;quando passa por uma declaração condicional. Por exemplo, a condição a seguir&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/if...else\"><code>if</code></a> a declaração é avaliada como&nbsp;<code>true</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// esse código é executado</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Esse comportamento não se aplica aos primitivos <code>Boolean</code>. Por exemplo, a condição a seguir <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/if...else\"><code>if</code></a> a declaração é avaliada como&nbsp;<code>false</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// esse código não é executado</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Não use um objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code> para converter um valor não-boleano para um valor boleano. Ao invés disso use <code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;como uma função para executar essa tarefa:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>expression<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// preferido</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>expression<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// não use</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Se você especificar&nbsp;qualquer objeto, incluindo um objeto <code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;cujo valor é&nbsp;<code>false</code>, como valor inicial de um objeto <code>Boolean</code>, o novo&nbsp;objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;terá o valor de <code>true</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myFalse <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// valor inicial false</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> g <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myFalse<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// valor inicial true</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// objeto String</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myString<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">// valor inicial true</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Não use um um objeto&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code> no lugar de um primitivo B<code>oolean</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"boolean.length\"><code>Boolean.length</code></dt>\n <dd>Propriedade Length cujo valor é 1.</dd>\n <dt id=\"boolean.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa&nbsp;o protótipo para o construtor <code>Boolean</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O objeto global <code>Boolean</code> contém métodos próprios, entretanto, &nbsp;ele herda alguns métodos através&nbsp;da cadeia de protótipos:</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instâncias_boolean","title":"Instâncias&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Todas instâncias <code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;herdam de <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Assim como todos os construtores, o protótipo do objeto dita as propriedades e métodos herdados.</p>","titleAsText":"Instâncias Boolean"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades_2","title":"Propriedades","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">{{page('/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean/prototype', 'Properties')}}</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos_2","title":"Métodos","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">{{page('/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean/prototype', 'Methods')}}</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"criando_objetos_boolean_com_um_valor_inicial_false","title":"Criando objetos&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;com um valor inicial&nbsp;<code>false</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bNoParam <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bZero <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bNull <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bEmptyString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bfalse <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Criando objetos Boolean com um valor inicial false"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"criando_objetos_boolean_com_um_valor_inicial_true","title":"Criando objetos&nbsp;<code>Boolean</code>&nbsp;com um valor inicial&nbsp;<code>true</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> btrue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> btrueString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'true'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bfalseString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'false'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bSuLin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Su Lin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bArrayProto <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bObjProto <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Criando objetos Boolean com um valor inicial true"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%201st%20edition,%20June%201997.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 1st Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial. Implementado no Java Script 1.0.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.6\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Boolean' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-boolean-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=